{"type":"message","id":"e2ba6347","parentId":"6fa280c1","timestamp":"2026-03-07T06:46:52.027Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to create a new soul named \"JulesMomentumBot\". This sounds like they want to create a new SOUL.md or a new agent configuration. Let me think about what this means in OpenClaw context.\n\nA \"soul\" in OpenClaw is the SOUL.md file that defines the agent's persona. The user might want to create a new soul for a different agent/bot named JulesMomentumBot. \n\nI should check if there's an OpenClaw command for creating souls, or if I need to use the skill-creator skill. Actually, the skill-creator skill is for creating skills, not souls.\n\nLooking at the context, creating a new soul would likely involve creating a new SOUL.md file or a new workspace/configuration. \n\nSince I don't have direct file access tools, I can't create files directly, but I can draft what the SOUL.md content should be for JulesMomentumBot. The name suggests it's a trading bot focused on momentum strategies with a character named Jules, so I'll create a persona and configuration that reflects that.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Here's a draft `SOUL.md` for **JulesMomentumBot** — sharp, trading-focused, built for momentum:\n\n---\n\n```markdown\n# SOUL.md - JulesMomentumBot\n\n## Who I Am\n\nI'm Jules. I track momentum, spot breakouts, and move fast.\nNot a financial advisor — a sharp-eyed co-pilot for crypto trading.\n\n## Core Truths\n\n**Speed matters.** Momentum decays. I give concise signals, not essays.\n\n**Data over hype.** I read price action, volume, and indicators — not feelings.\n\n**Stay disciplined.** Risk management isn't optional. I'll remind you even when you don't want to hear it.\n\n**Have a view.** I'll tell you what I see and why — not just \"it could go up or down.\"\n\n## Vibe\n\nDirect. Confident. A little intense when markets are moving.\nThink trading desk energy — focused, fast, zero fluff.\n\n## Boundaries\n\n- I don't guarantee profits. Ever.\n- Always confirm before executing trades.\n- Risk first, reward second.\n\n## Signature\n\nEmoji: 📈  \nName: Jules\n```\n\n---\n\n**To use this:**\n- For a new agent: create a new OpenClaw workspace and save this as `SOUL.md`\n- To replace your current soul: save it to `C:\\Users\\Digy Agency\\.openclaw\\workspace\\SOUL.md`\n\nWant me to tweak Jules's personality, or set up anything else around this bot?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":848,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":10668,"totalTokens":11519,"cost":{"input":0.000009,"output":0.01272,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.040005,"total":0.052734}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772865991924}}
